@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_uouaaf(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = ((wp.exp(v0 + 0.78) / wp.cos(v0 + 0.99)) / wp.sin(wp.cos(v1 + 0.30)))
    v0 = (wp.sin(0.91) * 0.11)
    v1 = wp.cos(wp.cos(0.90))
    v1 = wp.cos(tmp)
    v2 = (v1 / (wp.abs(tmp + 0.38) * (v1 + 0.95 * v1 + 0.75)))
    data[tid] = v0
